      "text": "+ consume broadcastSelection from useEditor()\n\n+ add to Workbook hooks:\n\naftSelectionChange: (sheetId, selection) => {\n  if (selection?.row.length && selection.column.length) {\n    broadcastSelection(\n      sheetId,\n      selection.row_focus ?? selection.row[0],\n      selection.column_focus ?? selection.column[0]\n    );\n  }\n}\n\nNOTE: this hook already exists in Workbook/index.tsx\n— just wire it to awareness.",
      "fontSize": 13, "fontFamily": 2, "textAlign": "left",
